<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy — AcquireTMT" %>

<section class="bg-brand-900 py-20 text-white sm:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl font-medium">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/60">Last updated: June 2026</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-10 px-4 leading-7 text-slate-600 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <p>
      This Privacy Policy explains how AcquireTMT ("we", "us") collects, uses, and protects information when you
      use our website, tools, and services (the "Service"). By using the Service you agree to this policy.
    </p>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-brand-900">Information we collect</h2>
      <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
        <li><strong>Information you provide:</strong> account details (name, email), information submitted to our tools (such as a company website, revenue, and profit), and details entered in lead or contact forms (name, email, phone, message).</li>
        <li><strong>Buyer profile information:</strong> if you join the Buyer Network, the acquisition criteria you provide (buyer type, industries, size, geography).</li>
        <li><strong>Information collected automatically:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages viewed, and similar usage data, including via cookies.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-brand-900">How we use information</h2>
      <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
        <li>To provide and operate the tools (valuation, market comps, buyer matching) and your account;</li>
        <li>To connect sellers with advisors and qualified buyers;</li>
        <li>To send service communications and, where permitted, relevant deal alerts;</li>
        <li>To improve the Service, prevent abuse, and comply with legal obligations.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-brand-900">Service providers we share with</h2>
      <p class="mt-3">We share information with vendors who process it on our behalf, including: Anthropic (AI analysis of website content for the tools), Apollo.io (company/buyer data), Google (sign-in), our hosting provider, and our email provider. We do not sell your personal information. We may disclose information where required by law or to protect our rights.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-brand-900">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="mt-3">We use essential cookies to keep you signed in and to operate the Service, and may use analytics cookies to understand usage. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-brand-900">Retention &amp; security</h2>
      <p class="mt-3">We retain information for as long as needed to provide the Service and meet legal obligations, then delete or anonymize it. We use reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect information, though no method of transmission or storage is completely secure.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-brand-900">Your rights</h2>
      <p class="mt-3">Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or restrict use of your personal information. To exercise these rights, contact us using the details below.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-brand-900">Changes &amp; contact</h2>
      <p class="mt-3">We may update this policy from time to time; the "Last updated" date reflects the latest version. Questions about this policy can be sent via our <%= link_to "contact page", contact_path, class: "font-semibold text-brand-500 hover:underline" %>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
